Erika Bailon
Hw5: Lighting
CSCI4229

Demonstrates basic lighting - Spend about 8 hours then found out my roof was lighting completely wrong 
and my Wall-E too so spend another 2 hours fixing the normalization of all components of their bodies.

Key bindings
  a/A		Toggles axes
  l         	Toggles lighting
  h/H        	Decrease/increase ambient light
  j/J        	Decrease/increase diffuse light
  k/K       	Decrease/increase specular light
  u/U       	Decrease/increase emitted light
  n/N        	Decrease/increase shininess
  g          	Toggles light movement
  []         	Lower/rise light
  M          	Toggles ortogonal/perspective projection
  +/-        	Change field of view of perspective
  arrows     	Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  	Zoom in and out
  0          	Reset view angle
  ESC        	Exit
